metadata.name: They label me an immigrant
metadata.description:
There are signs  of identity documents in my artworks

Personal Photo : A three by four vertical frame from opposite view, with nonsense face, showing one’s self-identity.
* By itself it is one of the official and Identity Documents.

Fingerprint : Bumps and dents on the fingertips skin.
* Greatest Identification Tool - everyone has their own unique fingerprint .

And Labeling…
The question is, “All of these Identification Tools, could give our Immigrants Identity ?!

-Selected photo of Black and white photography awards 2021 of LENSCULTURE-
